reviews.review_text:
Tenn Jed I know there is a cut in JED but wow does Jerry bend those strings toward the end of the tune.
It was a good year to live in Madison, Wisconsin between this and 2/15/73
The Weather Report Suite would have been the big news for the locals and in a really nice slot for this show!

Insane. This is a top 10 all time show for me. Dick obviously knew his shit, and I'm very thankful for him pointing me toward this show. This is some insane, freaky, out of this world type shit. Absolutely spectacular show.

Bobby rockin right to the end! Loving Bobby's vocal "flourishes" at the end of Saturday Night... so much better than the falcetto he adopted and tortured throughout the years!
Another I wasn't familiar with, maybe listen to it a couple of times over the years as I dug into late 73. Really good show, with some really interest explorations throughout! 
Definitely worth a run thru!
